{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01AkaVXZjDrBexcSAPteCZG3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the current state:\n\n**On /app vhost:**\n- admin: full permissions (.*,.*,.*) - OK for admin\n- ops-user: full permissions (.*,.*,.*) - WRONG: ops-user should have NO permissions on /app\n- app-user: configure=\"\", write=.*, read=.* - WRONG: configure is empty, should be .*\n\n**On /ops vhost:**\n- admin: full permissions (.*,.*,.*) - OK for admin\n- ops-user: NO permissions listed - WRONG: ops-user should have full permissions on /ops\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Add configure=.* to app-user on /app\n2. Remove ops-user's permissions from /app entirely\n3. Grant ops-user full permissions on /ops\n\nLet me apply these fixes now.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":705,"cache_read_input_tokens":28996,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":705},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0425fbf6-ef6f-4923-9d39-e41a4b12c0db","uuid":"ec16c58e-436d-4a4c-9485-e43a0662c277","request_id":"req_011CcLF2whXkDCRU6CiYwC7d"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01AkaVXZjDrBexcSAPteCZG3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issues are clear:\n- `app-user` on `/app`: `configure` is empty (should be `.*`)\n- `ops-user` on `/app`: has full permissions (should have none)\n- `ops-user` on `/ops`: has no permissions at all (should be full)\n\nFixing all three issues now."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":705,"cache_read_input_tokens":28996,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":705},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0425fbf6-ef6f-4923-9d39-e41a4b12c0db","uuid":"075ea9ae-9b7e-4761-abfa-1afba26fc6a5","request_id":"req_011CcLF2whXkDCRU6CiYwC7d"}
